title: FEB 11 2022 - TRUCKER UPDATES: PEOPLE VS THE REGIME
description:
The Convoy continues with good news: Ontario Premier Doug Ford to drop mandates, and  Christian crowdfunding website GiveSendGo has ignored Ontario’s attempt to shut down support for the canadian truckers, meanwhile new analytics show that inflation has hit up to 7.5% in the last year marking the highest it has been since 1982, abortions in Texas have fell 60% after one month since new law has taken effect, and Russia has agreed to a 30-year contract with China to supply gas via new pipeline. 



Here’s your Daily dose of Human Events with @JackPosobiec
